name: Lillymon (Digimon)
description:
Digimon Adventure 01 & 02 character representing Lillymon, an ultimate Digimon.
Lillymon evolves from Palmon / Togemon which is the partner of Tachikawa Mimi.

She's a kind and nature based Digimon which ressemble a female pixie.

modelVersions.name: digimon_lillymon - V2 - NAI
modelVersions.description:
LoRa mainly based on any anime screenshots of Lillymon I could find with as many angles possible.

Greatly increases the accurancy of Lillymon's features such as the boots, the arms and the wings.

I'm also incorporating part of the training datas (only manga and from the official books).

Trained upon the NAI model.

I consider this version to be the best of the V2 ones.
